{"tid":1305411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［美國巴絲入］寫信助攻人權法有template！！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:44:50.000Z","uid":194805,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1768cafd935a473833c93121d2f47eab1d757a","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:25:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">在美港人組織搞左個一人一信campaign助攻外國勢力推香港人權及民主法案</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9d88fe94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n幾個掣搞掂，全程由平台搞<span style=\"color: teal;\">組織唔會攞你資料</span><br />\n<br />\n大家寫完記住跟手整封去自己個state representative，呢個法案除左盧比奧個參議院法案仲有<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾議院法案</span>架<br />\n<br />\nFind your representative: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.house.gov/representatives/find-your-representative\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.house.gov%2Frepresentatives%2Ffind-your-representative&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=417eef17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.house.gov/representatives/find-your-representative</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越多co-sponsor越易成事啊！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再覺得你冇嘢可以做到<br />\n簽完再搵5個朋友 越多州越好<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">WE CONNECT</span></span>"},{"pid":"33a7fc409a3344d6ad3cd35a8f5d1543a4a484ea","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:25:59.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要睇醫生 我要投訴你\n我要報警 我想告佢 我係目擊證人 我要報案編號</code></pre>"},{"pid":"04dd5049ebb739a6551e50df9da8e242ba7ead09","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:27:09.000Z","msg":"【美國巴絲速速現身！】美國page 教人幫手推美國通過法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35f17ecc1bdb3969d6abd958ad10b1010fcd41a2","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"c365e857671779ccfb1551b40965e2159be61c07","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"1f46a4701b053aa1b7b3f1620e25c1e848990fa2","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:29:37.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"74f2a3162af8f1e2e64acddd3892829e08e04a22","tid":1305411,"uid":264915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa88041b0f3232ce7e8d91702867814cb37b5d4e","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"e8662f6cc9dc75a21a43f42cdffe8bb9013bbf3e","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:31:31.000Z","msg":"英文版方便傳道：<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Forum, Los Angeles, N. California Hong Kong Club, and NY4HK today launched a letter writing campaign to push for the congress to act on the proposed Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act (H.R. 3289, S. 1838).<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act aims to reaffirm the United States' commitment to support human rights of people of Hong Kong and democratization of the city's political system, by way of protection of citizens involved in peaceful protests and punishment of human rights violators within the capacity of the United States government. The bill currently has bipartisan support, with 9 co-sponsors in the House, and 8 co-sponsors in the Senate.<br />\n<br />\nAll American residents are encouraged to participate using the following link: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9d88fe94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019</a>"},{"pid":"98a850db34800a2c8cf78155caebff7ffd3dbbb6","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a5c168c0a8769ae74881cdab09cce7cffd79c7","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:32:22.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"a39b613c54c8a7a05ce6d6a851abb5a3098fd637","tid":1305411,"uid":194805,"like":0,"